· Replace original thinking, judgment, or decision-making
. Fabricate experience, results, metrics, or prior work
. Produce content that the candidate cannot explain or defend
. Circumvent the intent of the assessment

Candidates are fully accountable for all submitted work, regardless of whether Al was
used.
